    "excerpt":  "\u003cp\u003eWhite Knight Academy started with a simple observation: many parents and adult learners\u0026hellip;\u003c/p\u003e\n",
    "content":  "\t\t\u003cdiv data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"4785\" class=\"elementor elementor-4785\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00cd519 e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"00cd519\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5a88c38 elementor-drop-cap-yes elementor-drop-cap-view-default sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5a88c38\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{\u0026quot;drop_cap\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;yes\u0026quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eWhite Knight Academy started with a simple observation: many parents and adult learners want a clear way to \u003cstrong data-start=\"593\" data-end=\"615\"\u003elearn chess online\u003c/strong\u003e, but most resources feel scattered. You watch a few videos, try a puzzle here and there, maybe join a random stream — and still don’t know what to practice next. We’re shaping a structured path where \u003cstrong data-start=\"816\" data-end=\"840\"\u003eonline chess lessons\u003c/strong\u003e are not just content, but a guided process with real feedback, consistency, and measurable progress.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-65fb2ba e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"65fb2ba\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e2c100a sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e2c100a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"\u003eThe Real Problem\u003c/h5\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c2135b3 sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c2135b3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp data-start=\"966\" data-end=\"1277\"\u003eMost \u003cstrong data-start=\"971\" data-end=\"995\"\u003echess classes online\u003c/strong\u003e fall into one of two extremes: they’re either too casual (fun, but no direction) or too advanced (great content, but not designed for real beginners). For families, it’s even harder — kids often need a clear routine, short tasks, and a coach who keeps the learning fun and focused.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-49f4dc2 e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"49f4dc2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{\u0026quot;background_background\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;classic\u0026quot;}\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f29d2f sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5f29d2f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eEvery chess master was once a beginner.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8a9c996 e-con-full e-flex sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8a9c996\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-161968d elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget-divider--view-line sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"161968d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-divider\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\"elementor-divider-separator\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/span\u003e\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef48471 sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ef48471\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"\u003eIrving Chernev\u003c/h6\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc8ecb3 e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fc8ecb3\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3857903 sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3857903\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp data-start=\"1279\" data-end=\"1436\"\u003eThat’s why so many people search for \u003cstrong data-start=\"1316\" data-end=\"1347\"\u003echess classes for beginners\u003c/strong\u003e or \u003cstrong data-start=\"1351\" data-end=\"1377\"\u003ebeginner chess lessons\u003c/strong\u003e, start with motivation, and then stop after a few weeks:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul data-start=\"1437\" data-end=\"1554\"\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"1437\" data-end=\"1471\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1439\" data-end=\"1471\"\u003ethere’s no structured sequence\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"1472\" data-end=\"1507\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1474\" data-end=\"1507\"\u003ethere’s no feedback on mistakes\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"1508\" data-end=\"1554\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1510\" data-end=\"1554\"\u003ethere’s no plan that fits a weekly routine\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71bd0f2 e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"71bd0f2\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5054456 sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"5054456\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1009\" src=\"https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-7131\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552.jpg 1600w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-300x189.jpg 300w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-1024x646.jpg 1024w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-768x484.jpg 768w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-1536x969.jpg 1536w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-370x233.jpg 370w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-924x583.jpg 924w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-410x259.jpg 410w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-630x397.jpg 630w, https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-clickerhappy-510552-79x50.jpg 79w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" /\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7678f5f e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7678f5f\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c3ac5a sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7c3ac5a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"\u003eWhat We’re Creating\u003c/h5\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1002ad9 sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1002ad9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp data-start=\"1664\" data-end=\"1830\"\u003eOur goal is a platform where a \u003cstrong data-start=\"1695\" data-end=\"1725\"\u003echess course for beginners\u003c/strong\u003e actually feels like a course: step-by-step, predictable, and easy to follow — for kids and adults alike.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1832\" data-end=\"1861\"\u003eWhat we’re building around:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul data-start=\"1862\" data-end=\"2186\"\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"1862\" data-end=\"1936\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1864\" data-end=\"1936\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1864\" data-end=\"1889\"\u003eOnline chess coaching\u003c/strong\u003e with a clear weekly plan (not random topics)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"1937\" data-end=\"2028\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1939\" data-end=\"2028\"\u003eSmall-group sessions + optional \u003cstrong data-start=\"1971\" data-end=\"1993\"\u003echess tutor online\u003c/strong\u003e support when you need extra help\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2029\" data-end=\"2111\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2031\" data-end=\"2111\"\u003ePractical training: tactics, simple openings, strategy basics, and game review\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2112\" data-end=\"2186\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2114\" data-end=\"2186\"\u003eProgress tracking that shows what improved (and what still needs work)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2188\" data-end=\"2410\"\u003eThis will also connect directly to our membership packages — so you can choose a plan (monthly or yearly) and always know what you’re getting: live sessions, structured training, and guidance that keeps you moving forward.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2412\" data-end=\"2594\"\u003eIf you’d like to shape the first version, we’re opening Alpha/Beta testing soon. Comment \u003cstrong data-start=\"2501\" data-end=\"2512\"\u003e“ALPHA”\u003c/strong\u003e and tell us: \u003cstrong data-start=\"2526\" data-end=\"2543\"\u003ekids or adult\u003c/strong\u003e, and your current level (beginner / intermediate).\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t",
